Author: dragaynite
Text: EVERYTIME!! I always ask my dad to go get oreos when I’m craving them super bad and he refuses. But when I’m actively restricting and going to the gym I come home to a family pack of double stuff. It feels like sabotage >:(

Author: karmarell
Text: Yeah, it seems like a law. When I decide to buy binge food everything looks mehh and is expensive. As soon as I wanna start restricting I see the most appealing LEs for sale.
